response.overview: More Dirty debutantes vol. 124 goes through a reality check, check it out! It's all reality from beginning to end. First time exploration for all. Crystal and Rob have been long time friends, and before this DVD they never did more than a kiss. Watch them go further...the ending might even surprise ya! Hailey fits in with the early criteria of Dirty Debutante, and so does Mattie, both eager and both unique and sexual. Angel Angelino is an open minded free spirit, little wild and yet adorable and perky! MDD 124 is here. Please enjoy! Love, Ed Powers, Your Nasty Bro.
